 creating initiatives creating foundational cornerstone projects that reach across portfolio and assisting with company level hiring and activity third party relationship management vendor consolidation and combined purchasing power creates economies of scale and access to best in breed providers for the portfolio vista helps harness synergies by identifying purchasing trends products and service commonalities improving endtoend sourcing offering preferred vendor relations across the portfolio creates consistent methodologies and beneficial consistency and providing specialized services for niche needs news  awards  vista equity partners skip to main content x our firm about team careers approach philosophy value creation consulting group intelligence group strategies private equity credit public equity companies insights media press releases news  awards contact investor login media news  awards featured vista news   artificial intelligence how can industry leaders design the principles and technical standards into their products that benefit society as a whole vista ceo robert smith leads a panel on this question with ibm ceo ginni rometty microsoft ceo satya nadella mit media lab director joichi ito and healthtap ceo ron gutman at the world economic forum watch the video   smith job skills will be the next generation challenge robert smith founder and chief executive officer at vista equity partners discusses using technology to solve societys problems and the challenge of bringing skills and jobs to the next generation he speaks from the world economic forum in davos switzerland on bloomberg surveillance watch the video   at davos ibm chief predicts artificial intelligence won’t be a job killer while the technology will create obsolescence it may also create employment read more   report reaffirms generational tendencies at work for the first time in history many workplaces are experiencing up to five generations working together creating situations that present