 online event registration services vista has since acquired lanyon inc a software company based out of dallas texas with whom they merged a portion of active networks business solutions group bsg in september  vista announced its sale of microedge to blackbaud inc for  million in september  vista announced that it would acquire tibco software for  billion in june  vista acquired the assets of student information system from pearson plc which included powerschool a provider of k student information systems used by  million students in  countries in june  vista acquired mediaocean a software provider for the advertising industry in september  vista announced an agreement to acquire solera holdings a provider of data and software for the automotive and insurance industries for approximately  billion in march  vista announced its completion of this acquisition in june  vista announced an agreement to acquire marketo a marketing automation software company for approximately  billion it also announced an agreement to acquire ping identity a singlesign on digital security company for an undisclosed amountcitation needed in september  vista announced an agreement to acquire technology company infoblox for approximately  billion in cash in september  vista acquired regulatory datacorp a provider of counterparty risk and financial regulatory compliance data and software in november  the company acquired event management software company cvent for usd billion in may  vista acquired xactly corporation a leading provider of cloudbased incentive solutions in april  vista announced they were acquiring markettrack llc a provider of advertising ecommerce brand protection and other information to retailers brands manufacturers and others from los angelesbased private equity investor aurora capital group vista occasionally makes passive public equity investments in addition to investments in debt securities through its vista credit opportunities platform referencesedit  company overv