 billion in may  vista acquired xactly corporation a leading provider of cloudbased incentive solutions in april  vista announced they were acquiring markettrack llc a provider of advertising ecommerce brand protection and other information to retailers brands manufacturers and others from los angelesbased private equity investor aurora capital group vista occasionally makes passive public equity investments in addition to investments in debt securities through its vista credit opportunities platform referencesedit  company overview of vista equity partners bloomberg retrieved september     httpperacscomhecdowjonesprivateequityperformancerankingswhichfirmsgeneratedbestperformancefortheirinvestorsoverthepastyears  davis scott  blackhawk network holdings inc hawk shares bought by vista equity partners management llc wkrb news retrieved    vista equity partners crunchbase retrieved november     dawn lim march   vista equity sets  billion upper limit for new fund wall street journal retrieved october     melanie austria farmer march   bigmachines reels in  million cnet news retrieved october     bigmachines secures additional growth investment press release bigmachines inc september   retrieved october     oracle and bigmachines oracle web page retrieved october     julie bort october   source oracle paid over  million for bigmachines to grab more salesforce customers business insider retrieved october     sumtotal chooses rival bid from vista dealbook the new york times may   retrieved november     sumtotal july   deregistration of securities form s us securities and exchange commission retrieved november     us private equity firm vista equity partners pays m for financerelated software business microedge altassets july   retrieved november     advent software enters into definitive agreement for sale of microedge subsidiary to vista equity partners bostoncom july   retrieved november     ingrid lunden june   software recruitment giant bullhorn acquired by vista equit